ildren (Ni\u00f1os) who remained in Great Britain, 1948\"</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Names+of+Basque+Children+%28Ni%C3%B1os%29+who+remained+in+Great+Britain%2C+1948&amp;rft.aulast=Hoare&amp;rft.aufirst=Gerald&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.basquechildren.org%2Freference%2Fbackground1948&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEvacuation+of+children+in+the+Spanish+Civil+War\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.basquechildren.org/colonies/history\">\"History of the Colonies\"</a>. <i>Basque Children of '37 Association UK</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">5 August</span> 2016</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Basque+Children+of+%2737+Association+UK&amp;rft.atitle=History+of+the+Colonies&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.basquechildren.org%2Fcolonies%2Fhistory&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEvacuation+of+children+in+the+Spanish+Civil+War\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Evacuation_of_children_in_the_Spanish_Civil_War&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.basquechildren.org/\">\"Basque Children of '37 Association UK\"</a>. <i>basquechildren.org</i>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=basquechildren.org&amp;rft.atitle=Basque+Children+of+%2737+Association+UK&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.basquechildren.org%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEvacuation+of+children+in+the+Spanish+Civil+War\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://histclo.com/essay/war/ww2/camp/eur/ea/scw/ref/scwr-bas.html\">\"The Spanish Civil War: Basque Refugee Children (1936\u201339)\"</a>. <i>Historical Boys' Clothing</i>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Historical+Boys%27+Clothing&amp;rft.atitle=The+Spanish+Civil+War%3A+Basque+Refugee+Children+%281936%E2%80%9339%29&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fhistclo.com%2Fessay%2Fwar%2Fww2%2Fcamp%2Feur%2Fea%2Fscw%2Fref%2Fscwr-bas.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEvacuation+of+children+in+the+Spanish+Civil+War\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li></ul>\n<div role=\"navigation\" class=\"navbox\" aria-labelledby=\"Spanish_Civil_War_(1936\u201339)\" style=\"padding:3px\"><table class=\"nowraplinks collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;color:inherit\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist navbar mini\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template:Spanish_Civil_War\" title=\"Template:Spanish Civil War\"><abbr title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">v</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template_talk:Spanish_Civil_War\" title=\"Template talk:Spanish Civil War\"><